  "description": {
    "zh": "骨折不仅仅是疼，它有时候能直接把你命搭进去。你想想，跑路的时候腿突然一断，或者你正在穿越开阔地，结果就趴那儿起不来了。止痛药当然能稍微缓解点，但你得知道怎么去处理骨折。\n\n你可以用夹板来处理手臂或腿部的骨折。我可不建议你自己去试着断几条骨头来练练，信我，真没这个必要。无论如何，学学怎么在突袭中用夹板治疗骨折吧。祝你好运。",
    "en": "Breaking limbs is more than just painful, it can lead to your death in some cases, I mean... It's not ideal to get your leg broken while running away from someone, or travelling through open areas. Painkillers can help with that to some degree of course, but you need to know how to fix a fracture.\n\nYou can use splints to treat a fracture in your arms or legs. I wouldn't suggest you hurt yourself to break a leg or two, trust me. Anyway, learn to treat broken limbs while using some form of splint, alright? Good luck out there."
  },
